===== Dashboard =====

This class is designed to work with dashboards. 

Object references: \\
  * [[manual:api:reference:dashboard:object#dashboard|Dashboard]]
  * [[manual:api:reference:dashboard:object#dashboard_widget|Dashboard widget]]
  * [[manual:api:reference:dashboard:object#dashboard_widget_field|Dashboard widget field]]
  * [[manual:api:reference:dashboard:object#dashboard_user_group|Dashboard user group]]
  * [[manual:api:reference:dashboard:object#dashboard_user|Dashboard user]]

Available methods: \\
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:dashboard:create|dashboard.create]]'' - creating new dashboards
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:dashboard:delete|dashboard.delete]]'' - deleting dashboards
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:dashboard:get|dashboard.get]]'' - retrieving dashboards
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:dashboard:update|dashboard.update]]'' - updating dashboards